    • BoardGame

      public BoardGame(Long sn, String name, String brand, double price, int availableCount, int ageAppropriate, int minPlayer, int maxPlayer, String designer)
      this is a copy constructor that includes the parameters needed for a board game sn, name, brand, price, availableCount, and ageAppropriate are called from the superclass
      Parameters:
      sn - serial number
      name - name of the board game
      brand - brand of the board game
      price - price of the board game
      availableCount - how many board games they have
      ageAppropriate - the minimum age limit of the game
      minPlayer - the minimum number of players needed to play
      maxPlayer - the maximum number of players that can play
      designer - the designer of the game
